		1. I had no chance to attend any Names subgroup meeting! Jessie canceled the one originally planned on Monday morning (for which I had canceled our own SDD meeting originally also scheduled Mo morning to make time so that I and others could participate at least in one Names-subgroup meeting). On the weekend the SDD group convened in parallel to the names session.
